id":100642,"uid":242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T21:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打想要咩功效</blockquote><br />\n冷靜 異性緣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議帶白晶冷靜左自己先<br />\n<br />\n感情係未拍過拖定失左戀定其他？<br />\n要睇詳細情況先幫到你</blockquote><br />\n未拍過拖"},{"pid":"c605bd5d417d72bc8fbce3e07308e9dcc000de07","tid":100642,"uid":26276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實粒水晶種類要對自己有影響<br />\n咁不如真係戴水晶好過啦<br />\n<br />\nPs用緊金屬嘅金擺<br />\n<br />\n求完整教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯 同埋最好親身去揀合眼緣先work<br />\n靈擺作用係帶領你，所以會影響磁場，唔太建議用<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係專家 略知一二 大家交流下"},{"pid":"da2295f142fc81bc749d8bd7f36db5a7ae9977f0","tid":100642,"uid":18628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"帶緊金髮晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係都好似冇乜用"},{"pid":"3075d9247cb1e2ea2b7af0f2f09b18467007d695","tid":100642,"uid":26276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n冷靜 異性緣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議帶白晶冷靜左自己先<br />\n<br />\n感情係未拍過拖定失左戀定其他？<br />\n要睇詳細情況先幫到你</blockquote><br />\n未拍過拖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未拍過拖可以試下草莓晶/粉玉髓紅紋石<br />\n巴打唔想帶粉色珠都可以揀月亮石"},{"pid":"57857f80dc6ebc6695faedbe54515f8c24792a01","tid":100642,"uid":26276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶緊金髮晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係都好似冇乜用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n久唔久淨化下佢 <br />\nwork既會feel到手痺（聽朋友講 我都有試過）<br />\n<br />\n之前同女朋友鬧交帶過月亮石feel到手痺 <br />\n而且帶左關係都有好左<br />\n最近好亂又好衝動同女朋友講左分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢有留我但我覺得對佢唔住 自己未夠好<br />\n想冷靜完自己先搵返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以買左白晶加超級七 前者令自己清醒冷靜 後者功能全面又可以加強白晶效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d346041f90c20c0df3c7ec8e73745c13bb430cce","tid":100642,"uid":18628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>帶緊金髮晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係都好似冇乜用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n久唔久淨化下佢 <br />\nwork既會feel到手痺（聽朋友講 我都有試過）<br />\n<br />\n之前同女朋友鬧交帶過月亮石feel到手痺 <br />\n而且帶左關係都有好左<br />\n最近好亂又好衝動同女朋友講左分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢有留我但我覺得對佢唔住 自己未夠好<br />\n想冷靜完自己先搵返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以買左白晶加超級七 前者令自己清醒冷靜 後者功能全面又可以加強白晶效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶左成個禮拜都冇乜料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪我太心急"},{"pid":"503a60dd8846d05d40b29dad219222a1109b9a25","tid":100642,"uid":70481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:55:57.000Z","msg":"有冇舖頭推薦下+1"},{"pid":"7bd8f02ec6cba896e605257606d8c667a32a9c22","tid":100642,"uid":6668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>帶緊金髮晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係都好似冇乜用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n久唔久淨化下佢 <br />\nwork既會feel到手痺（聽朋友講 我都有試過）<br />\n<br />\n之前同女朋友鬧交帶過月亮石feel到手痺 <br />\n而且帶左關係都有好左<br />\n最近好亂又好衝動同女朋友講左分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢有留我但我覺得對佢唔住 自己未夠好<br />\n想冷靜完自己先搵返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以買左白晶加超級七 前者令自己清醒冷靜 後者功能全面又可以加強白晶效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶左成個禮拜都冇乜料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪我太心急</blockquote><br />\n唔同人既磁場都唔同，有人大半年先work有人一戴就work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家都戴緊月亮石，真係發少左脾氣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家想入多條金曜石貔貅同s7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715899a320e507b4f6c7f525a72753f02fe7f9c5","tid":100642,"uid":6668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:05:11.000Z","msg":"Btw 靈擺我以前買過一條白晶，主要係拎黎問問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但至從比我跌爆左就冇再帶過，其實都幾唔方便<br />\n如果純粹想催運都係手鍊啦"},{"pid":"68583d73d3a99788238829d9f57e96f06731b49d","tid":100642,"uid":26276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n久唔久淨化下佢 <br />\nwork既會feel到手痺（聽朋友講 我都有試過）<br />\n<br />\n之前同女朋友鬧交帶過月亮石feel到手痺 <br />\n而且帶左關係都有好左<br />\n最近好亂又好衝動同女朋友講左分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢有留我但我覺得對佢唔住 自己未夠好<br />\n想冷靜完自己先搵返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以買左白晶加超級七 前者令自己清醒冷靜 後者功能全面又可以加強白晶效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶左成個禮拜都冇乜料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪我太心急</blockquote><br />\n唔同人既磁場都唔同，有人大半年先work有人一戴就work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家都戴緊月亮石，真係發少左脾氣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家想入多條金曜石貔貅同s7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貔貅有朋友帶過work!!<br />\n但後期帶到斷左繩 話擋左災 好似係"},{"pid":"7bd655e0927b0c33f9ddb05f3c2383b2b52064ab","tid":100642,"uid":57927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"想長輩緣好啲應該戴咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63ddf05cda584b2b812692b7932a9cd0c58224c","tid":100642,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"粉晶其實係咪唔會旺姻緣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n帶咗一個月異性緣真係好咗但無個有feel"},{"pid":"ed5e693e840c7635678ec645a0d2733416385a3e","tid":100642,"uid":26276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>粉晶其實係咪唔會旺姻緣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n帶咗一個月異性緣真係好咗但無個有feel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旺 但通常爛桃花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7285523942d3fa71145e3c51fd15cf856821c5d1","tid":100642,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:23:07.000Z","msg":"有咩水晶可以帶右手<br />\n想降低暴燥同抑鬱心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a85c2c52e4df6a8cd66911dd77c050479c6661","tid":100642,"uid":5791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩水晶可以帶右手<br />\n想降低暴燥同抑鬱心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係新q,但呢個問題唔係咁正確，水晶原理係左入右出，所以睇你想要啲咩，我帶開黑曜石，防小人同輸出啲負能量呀，唔好嘅野，所以係帶右手。<br />\n又例如有d 晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幫你集中力好d 人緣好啲，果啲就帶左手。<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2544dbaf67abe3342981a1514860ca8795cd72","tid":100642,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議帶白晶冷靜左自己先<br />\n<br />\n感情係未拍過拖定失左戀定其他？<br />\n要睇詳細情況先幫到你</blockquote><br />\n未拍過拖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未拍過拖可以試下草莓晶/粉玉髓紅紋石<br />\n巴打唔想帶粉色珠都可以揀月亮石</blockquote><br />\n見有平有貴,點樣分月亮石真假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e3f75719052b46b2af1660c21bd4a0899a3672","tid":100642,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有咩水晶可以帶右手<br />\n想降低暴燥同抑鬱心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係新q,但呢個問題唔係咁正確，水晶原理係左入右出，所以睇你想要啲咩，我帶開黑曜石，防小人同輸出啲負能量呀，唔好嘅野，所以係帶右手。<br />\n又例如有d 晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幫你集中力好d 人緣好啲，果啲就帶左手。<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身有條黑曜 唔係幾掂<br />\n想買條帶右手 因為左手帶錶<br />\n想知有冇帶右手 平靜心情之類"},{"pid":"7f1b59e19a620ca524ec41c38b4b3ed32bf8984f","tid":100642,"uid":68488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T07:48:29.000Z","msg":"之前有條金曜貔貅，去紋拳頭老虎的時候 條鏈斷咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eff60ddc36225be41f0c6cbaecd8fb57eadbbe","tid":100642,"uid":68488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打想要咩功效</blockquote><br />\n冷靜 異性緣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議帶白晶冷靜左自己先<br />\n<br />\n感情係未拍過拖定失左戀定其他？<br />\n要睇詳細情況先幫到你</blockquote><br />\n分咗手 我提出的"},{"pid":"e019ac5979308029271360bcd0d9720c4730b6de","tid":100642,"uid":26276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n冷靜 異性緣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議帶白晶冷靜左自己先<br />\n<br />\n感情係未拍過拖定失左戀定其他？<br />\n要睇詳細情況先幫到你</blockquote><br />\n分咗手 我提出的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然有啲錯台feel 但介唔介意講詳情<br />\n同埋有帶開水晶？<br />\n<br />\n<del>我衰衝動又唔識諗都提左分手 後悔緊</del>"},{"pid":"0f219b6a9235dd9f066122336abae6cdcfc8f594","tid":100642,"uid":68488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議帶白晶冷靜左自己先<br />\n<br />\n感情係未拍過拖定失左戀定其他？<br />\n要睇詳細情況先幫到你</blockquote><br />\n分咗手 我提出的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然有啲錯台feel 但介唔介意講詳情<br />\n同埋有帶開水晶？<br />\n<br />\n<del>我衰衝動又唔識諗都提左分手 後悔緊</del></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家手有兩條 一條黃虎眼（冇咩感應 一條人造石"},{"pid":"d3ae2dc370e66609f8464231cc181dd568596928","tid":100642,"uid":26276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n分咗手 我提出的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然有啲錯台feel 但介唔介意講詳情<br />\n同埋有帶開水晶？<br />\n<br />\n<del>我衰衝動又唔識諗都提左分手 後悔緊</del></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家手有兩條 一條黃虎眼（冇咩感應 一條人造石</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黃虎眼有利事業<br />\n唔知既巴打咩事分手同分左幾耐 唔敢亂推你買<br />\n再加上本身有黃虎眼 你又想冷靜又異性緣<br />\n建議唔好亂帶姻緣晶住<br />\n可以好似我咁加條s7帶一陣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人唔建議帶好多唔同功效野係身"},{"pid":"7713f807a56b20f348866ce175ed7827eab6a589","tid":100642,"uid":50376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"靈擺我之前有條係黑曜石既，後尾係商務買左本靈擺書，隨書送個條金屬既我覺得感應好過黑曜石所以而家用金屬個條多<br />\n<br />\n如果你係想改善自己磁場呀乜乜物物個啲真係戴手鏈仲好，靈擺係用黎問問題就好啲"},{"pid":"5e8baca9772dab397d1a197a5e7efc5be3533136","tid":100642,"uid":242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n帶左成個禮拜都冇乜料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪我太心急</blockquote><br />\n唔同人既磁場都唔同，有人大半年先work有人一戴就work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家都戴緊月亮石，真係發少左脾氣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家想入多條金曜石貔貅同s7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貔貅有朋友帶過work!!<br />\n但後期帶到斷左繩 話擋左災 好似係</blockquote><br />\n我戴月亮石頸連，點先知feel到有效，我手戴彩幽靈真係有料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7270415281758e228a2cf3b838281023141f4c36","tid":100642,"uid":26276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有咩水晶可以帶右手<br />\n想降低暴燥同抑鬱心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係新q,但呢個問題唔係咁正確，水晶原理係左入右出，所以睇你想要啲咩，我帶開黑曜石，防小人同輸出啲負能量呀，唔好嘅野，所以係帶右手。<br />\n又例如有d 晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幫你集中力好d 人緣好啲，果啲就帶左手。<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身有條黑曜 唔係幾掂<br />\n想買條帶右手 因為左手帶錶<br />\n想知有冇帶右手 平靜心情之類</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以試下紫水晶"},{"pid":"b1aea70b75f5804e0b233b1245e8b18e966f36e5","tid":100642,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係新q,但呢個問題唔係咁正確，水晶原理係左入右出，所以睇你想要啲咩，我帶開黑曜石，防小人同輸出啲負能量呀，唔好嘅野，所以係帶右手。<br />\n又例如有d 晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幫你集中力好d 人緣好啲，果啲就帶左手。<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身有條黑曜 唔係幾掂<br />\n想買條帶右手 因為左手帶錶<br />\n想知有冇帶右手 平靜心情之類</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以試下紫水晶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紫色少紅 偏好女性仲有咩色介紹？<br />\nFor男帶"},{"pid":"fbc4f7af38da4b1db296cc5f314690bc0feb73da","tid":100642,"uid":25483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實粒水晶種類要對自己有影響<br />\n咁不如真係戴水晶好過啦<br />\n<br />\nPs用緊金屬嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">靈</span>擺<br />\n<br />\n求完整教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ba874393534b72ae3a009a077a8bcdb1ed11771","tid":100642,"uid":25483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靈擺我之前有條係黑曜石既，後尾係商務買左本靈擺書，隨書送個條金屬既我覺得感應好過黑曜石所以而家用金屬個條多<br />\n<br />\n如果你係想改善自己磁場呀乜乜物物個啲真係戴手鏈仲好，靈擺係用黎問問題就好啲</blockquote><br />\n求書名同封面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7da3e8c64d8b1948dc264e6da2aac587b25e4aa","tid":100642,"uid":6668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n帶左成個禮拜都冇乜料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪我太心急</blockquote><br />\n唔同人既磁場都唔同，有人大半年先work有人一戴就work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家都戴緊月亮石，真係發少左脾氣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家想入多條金曜石貔貅同s7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貔貅有朋友帶過work!!<br />\n但後期帶到斷左繩 話擋左災 好似係</blockquote><br />\n其實仲想買草莓晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但本身已經有條月亮石<br />\n草莓晶同月亮石功效好似差唔多咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea99344b04ab65fe50d065aea39499cf7e29f8a","tid":100642,"uid":77999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:06:19.000Z","msg":"想問下 我帶開金髮晶頸鏈 平時都有帶開同擺係個座到淨化下既，但呢排帶佢都自己跌落尼。同埋 好似無咩幫助咁，仲可以點搞搞佢<br />\n利申：仲有帶粉晶同黑髮晶"},{"pid":"0aad9eb56f1f1c46f63bfbd3593e613f48b9977e","tid":100642,"uid":49295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GF8Y8sf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGF8Y8sf.jpg&h=d9fa9024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搵到呢條$350,有無熟水晶既巴絲幫眼睇下值唔值得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" clas